snippet.title: Claustrophobic Nights - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Claustrophobic Nights is a recreation of Crawlspace 2 in the style of FNaF Help Wanted with multiplayer included. In the game, you crawl through tight spaces and solve various puzzles whilst evading animatronics in order to beat the night.
